-- Teenager Killed as Rioters Attack Police Patrol, Bahrain Says
-- B y   W a e l   M a h d i
-- 2012-09-29T16:38:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-29/teenager-killed-as-rioters-attack-police-patrol-bahrain-says.html
In Bahrain, 17-year-old Ali Hussein
Neama was killed yesterday as rioters attacked a police patrol
in Sadad village, the country’s Information Affairs Authority
said in an e-mailed statement today.  The attackers were armed with Molotov cocktails and steel
rods, according to the statement. Bahrain’s Public Prosecution
office started an investigation into the attack, it said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wael Mahdi in Manama at 
 wmahdi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
